---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Women's Self Defence Classes Perth | Jan de Jong Martial Arts" description="Women's self defence courses in Perth. Learn practical self-defence techniques, situational awareness & confidence building. Experienced female instructor. Book your course today.">
  <Hero 
    title="Self Defence" 
    backgroundImage="/images/self-defence-img.png"
    showCta={false}
  />
  
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-width max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                <div class="avatar">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">💪</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-4">
                  <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading uppercase mb-2">Women's Self Defence</h1>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">Personal Safety & Empowerment</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                <blockquote class="text-xl text-primary font-semibold mb-6 pl-4 border-l-4 border-primary">
                  "Self defence is a basic life skill which most women will find useful at least once in their life time."
                </blockquote>
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading uppercase mb-4">Practical Skills for Real Situations</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  You will be taught a number of self defence techniques that can be easily learnt and used against a wide variety of attacks. These techniques are based on Ju Jutsu principles and emphasise efficiency over strength.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  You don't have to be strong, big, athletic, flexible or aggressive to be effective. Our course covers ways of avoiding and diffusing potentially dangerous situations, providing alternatives to physical confrontation whenever possible.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-hover text-white">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-4">Course Benefits</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <span class="mr-3">🏆</span>
                <span>Build Confidence</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <span class="mr-3">🚫</span>
                <span>Avoid Dangerous Situations</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <span class="mr-3">🔐</span>
                <span>Practical Techniques</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <span class="mr-3">👩‍🏫</span>
                <span>Female Instructor</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card bg-accent">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-heading uppercase mb-4">Who Should Attend?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>Women of all ages</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>No fitness requirements</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>No prior experience needed</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>Corporate groups welcome</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>Individual or group sessions</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading uppercase mb-4 flex items-center">
              <div class="avatar">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">🖐️</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-3">
Empowerment Through Knowledge
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              As with other life skills such as water and road safety, your knowledge of self defence may one day ensure the safety of your family, friends and other members of the community.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Everyone has a basic right to feel free without being constrained by the fear of violence. Learning self defence and taking sensible precautions enables you to more freely exercise that right.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading uppercase mb-4 flex items-center">
              <div class="avatar">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">🤝</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-3">
Supportive Environment
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Classes are run in an easy, friendly and relaxed atmosphere with time for participants to discuss individual issues with the instructor at the end of class.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Everyone works to their own capabilities and there is never any expectation that you should do anything you do not feel comfortable with.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading uppercase mb-6 text-center">Course Details</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading uppercase mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="mr-2 text-primary">📦</span>
              What's Included
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>12 hours instruction over 6 weeks</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>Experienced female instructor</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>Comprehensive course notes</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>Use of training facilities 6 days a week</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>1 FREE month of membership</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-primary">✓</span>
                <span>50% discount on further courses</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading uppercase mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="mr-2 text-primary">🎯</span>
              Course Options
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="font-heading uppercase mb-2">Group Bookings</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">5 for the price of 4! Perfect for friends or workplace groups.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="font-heading uppercase mb-2">Private Sessions</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">One-on-one lessons tailored to your specific needs.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="font-heading uppercase mb-2">Corporate Training</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Customized programs for workplace safety.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-primary font-semibold">🎉 Early Bird Discount: Book 2 weeks before start date!</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Level 1 must be completed prior to Level 2</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-hover p-8 rounded-lg text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">TAKE CONTROL OF YOUR SAFETY</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
          Join our Women's Self Defence course and gain the confidence and skills to protect yourself. 
          Learn from experienced female instructors in a supportive environment.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
          <Button href="/free-trial" class="bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100">Book Your Course</Button>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-white hover:text-gray-200 underline">Questions? Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>